To politics now and a section of ODM leaders are demanding that the party picks its presidential flagbearer within one month. The leaders argue that this is crucial to enable the party to prepare well for the 2022 general election. This was said in Mombasa today during a meeting between ODM leader Raila Odinga and some coast leaders. Raila who attended Eid Al Adha celebrations said plans to change the constitution is still in course as Tobias Chanji reports